Author: TonyL#3577
Content:
In cli just use:
to transfer warrior `./komodo-cli -ac_name=ROGUE tokentransfer playertokenid destpubkey 1`
to transfer funds `./komodo-cli -ac_name=ROGUE sendtoaddress address amount`
